        "description": "Typical beam diameters for precision cleaning; smaller for fine details, larger for area coverage. 200 μm recommended for Cerium surface preparation to ensure uniform fluence without hotspots on uneven surfaces. Source: Equipment specifications from Trumpf and SPI Lasers for 1064 nm cleaning heads."
